				<main role="main" class=""><article class="main-content"><h1 class="">Welcome</h1>
        <h2 class="">A Greater Future Awaits!</h2>
        <p class="">Welcome to Synergy Public School! We are a free, public charter school serving families in the urban core of Phoenix, Arizona. We are dedicated to providing all children with a challenging, child-centered education that fosters their love of learning and prepares them for a productive future.</p>
        <p class="">Take some time to browse our website and get to know our <a href="/Choose_Us" title="" alt="" target="_self">amazing school</a> and <a href="/Administration" title="" alt="" target="_self">staff</a>. We offer a <a href="/Academics" title="" alt="" target="_self">challenging curriculum</a> and have a wide variety of <a href="/Student_Services" title="" alt="" target="_self">programs</a> available to our students and families. Please <a href="/Contact_Us" title="" alt="" target="_self">contact us</a> if you have any questions. We look forward to hearing from you!</p>
        <h2 class="">A Message from Our Directors</h2>
        <p class="">Welcome to Synergy!</p>
        <p class="">Synergy is a Greek word that describes what happens when two individual forces combine to make something bigger or more effective. And that’s what we are! Together, we are Synergy. Together, we are investing in our children’s future and preparing them for something greater.</p>
        <p class="">Thank you for your interest in Synergy. We look forward to meeting with you, but in the meantime, please take a few minutes to browse our website and learn more about us. You can even <a href="/Online-Application" title="" alt="" target="_self" class="">enroll online</a>! If you have questions or need help with your enrollment documents, <a href="/Contact_Us" title="" alt="" target="_self">please let us know</a>. We’re happy to help.</p>
        <p class="">Sincerely,</p>
        <p class="signature">Lori Weiss and Melissa McKinsey</p>
        <p class="">Executive Directors</p>
