<p class="">We would like to announce the Synergy Public Schools teacher pay increase for the 2019–2020 school year. Please see the information below.</p>
<div class="pom-container"><ul>
<li class="">The average salary of all teachers employed in the budget year 2020 - $46,225.00</li>
<li class="">The average salary of all teachers employed in the budget year 2019 - $44,424.00</li>
<li class="">The increase in average teacher salary from the prior year 2019 - $1,801.00</li>
<li class="">The percentage increase - 4.1%. </li>
<li class="">The average salary of all teachers employed in FY 2018 - $40,364</li>
<li class="">Total percentage increase in average teacher salary since FY 2018 - 14.5%</li>
</ul></div>
