			<h2>COVID-19 UPDATE</h2>
			<p></p>
<div class="">
<p class="p1" style="margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(69, 69, 69);">COVID-19 UPDATE<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></p>
<p class="p2" style="margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); min-height: 14px;"><br></p>
<p class="p1" style="margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(69, 69, 69);">Good Afternoon Synergy Families, we would like to keep you up to date with the recent changes to school closures due to the Coronavirus.  Yesterday, Governor Doug Ducey and Superintendent of Public Instruction Kathy Hoffman announced the extension of Arizona school closures through the end of the school year. We are extremely saddened by this news but want to assure you that we will continue to serve breakfast and lunch meals to anyone who is 18 years of age or under.  Meals will continue to be distributed in front of the school office as a drive through service Monday - Thursday at 9:00am – 11:00am.  You will receive both breakfast and lunch at that time.  We miss you all and hope you are safe and healthy.  </p>
